::: {#5ba3fd42 .cell execution_count=15}
``` {.python .cell-code}
tiles = set([k.split(".")[0] for k in l2_item.assets.keys() if k.endswith("BOA")])
tile_x = set(int(tile[1:5]) for tile in tiles)
tile_y = set(int(tile[7:]) for tile in tiles)
tile_x, tile_y
```

